wizhelp trans
Command: trans
Argument: name
 
Transport a player or NPC to you.  Be warned, you are only allowed
to trans a player that is within the city limits.  Do not trans
players to get them out of tough situations unless you know for
a FACT that there is a bug in the room that is preventing them
from leaving.  Transing players to provide a quick way back to
town would be seriously frowned upon.
 
